data.name: DataFlavor
desc: Each instance represents the concept of a data format as it would appear on a clipboard, or during drag and drop.

items.name: MimeType
lines: The MIME content-type (type/subtype) string describing the data format of the object to transfer.
MimeType must conform to Rfc2045 and Rfc2046)

items.name: HumanPresentableName
lines: A human presentable name for the data format.

items.name: DataType
lines: The type of the object to transfer, for example, XOutputStream.
